# 📝 To-Do List CLI (Python)

A simple command-line To-Do List application built using Python.

## 🚀 Features

* Add tasks
* View all tasks
* Delete tasks
* Simple CLI interface

## 🧠 Concepts Used

* Lists
* Functions
* Loops
* Conditionals
* User input handling

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
python main.py
```

## 📌 Example

```
--- TO-DO LIST ---
1. Add Task
2. View Tasks
3. Delete Task
4. Exit
```

## 🎯 Goal

This project is part of my Python learning journey to build real-world applications step by step.

## 📅 Week 5 Focus

* Writing modular code
* Working with lists
* Building CLI applications

